        {
            "title": "今日我咁睇｜美伊談判有反覆 市場反應冷靜 恒指26000成支持｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jeYiEuIB6J8EQjz9zh6JDQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/6725994bd9bb8c8d772ce59a3dfbbe6c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><ol class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊談判未有成果，雙方亦在互相討價還價的階段，但畢竟談判未完，戰火力度亦降低，形勢仍向好。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價昨日反彈，但未到小編談及的90元分界線，而美股反應冷靜，雖然未有連升，但跌幅相對累積升幅微。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股方面，AI大模型股仍是小編所好，整體大市亦偏好，但若買指數則值博率一般。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">指數方面，預計恆指在企穩26000點後，該位阻力變支持，短期內或有望試26500至26800點。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恆指牛熊證街貨，牛證比例仍與熊證接近，雖然牛證較多但屬偏低水平，相反理論亦偏好。</p></li></ol></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%8D%E8%A6%86-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E5%86%B7%E9%9D%9C-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%8726000%E6%88%90%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000390.html",
